"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:18:02.000Z","msg":"查完未呀屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"Announcements<br />\n<br />\nAnnouncements relevant to this election will be placed here.<br />\n<br />\n21/04/2020<br />\nBy the deadline for submission of complaints a small number had been received. As per paragraph 12.3 of the election regulations, the Election Officer and the Acting Dean of Students have investigated these and concluded that the election result as already announced should stand. The Election Officer has therefore now submitted the name of the elected full-time student to the Council for appointment."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"finally <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c0d1461182e9dd272559dc0fb206c83b25312a","tid":1981955,"uid":195894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"以後香港咪撚再選舉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接宣布一國一制啦"}]}